{"tid":129970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp新增閱後即焚功能","createTime":"2017-02-22T04:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T02:56:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa09987de3a8537abf0b050cd098c63aa965ded","tid":129970,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170222/19936296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19936296&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1QCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bc7508a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19936296&h=9708a991\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170222/19936296</a><br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp新增閱後即焚功能<br />\n<br />\n80,922<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】WhatsApp（圖）再有大更新！是次更新個人狀態（Status），用戶以後除了文字及Emoji外，更可以分享照片、視頻和GIF動畫。連同WhatsApp，facebook旗下四大應用程式均以加入「閱後即焚」24小時的限時動態功能。<br />\nfacebook去年8月於旗下Instagram，推出與Snapchat的Live Stories幾乎一模一樣的功能，外界認為facebook將Snapchat功能「照抄」，公司管理層亦曾公開解畫，指並非「抄襲」，但承認加入由Snapchat開創的新功能模式。<br />\n至於今次WhatsApp的更新亦大同小異，Status由以往只可用文字及Emoji，變成可分享照片、視頻和GIF動畫，更可加上手繪等，而所有內容都將在24小時後消失。WhatsApp與其他平台的分別在於，WhatsApp可以分享GIF圖，另外片長可長達45秒。<br />\n一如以往，WhatsApp更新的新功能將分階段向各地用家推出。<br />\n■記者梁偉聰  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n有善信瞓街4日數百人冒雨排隊　市民求財不問財爺問觀音<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n《侍女圖．積琪蓮》等13作品破天荒外借　畢加索「最後情人」港首展出"},{"pid":"dbd92ca759d1810b7a6c070b82c0e18367498b73","tid":129970,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"Status由以往只可用文字及Emoji，變成可分享照片、視頻和GIF動畫，更可加上手繪等，而所有內容都將在24小時後消失。<br />\n<br />\nStatus ??"},{"pid":"fe6fbd9afb8bbb7b573dcfd1e1e87b86de0c4388","tid":129970,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" clas